§ Notation ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Let $f: 𝗥^d → 𝗥$ a density. ⦉

  ‖ For $i, j = 1, …, d$ and $i ≠ j$, let $f_{i |j}: 𝗥^2 →
    𝗥$ satisfy
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ f_{ij}(ξ, γ) = f_{i |j}(ξ, γ)f_j(γ) ⦉
    ⦉
    for $ξ, γ ∈ 𝗥$. ⦉
⦉

